{"tid":1440194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬抄團隊/文宣組請入！！]我宣報下一個回合應該咁做！！！","createTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:05.000Z","uid":68667,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e7625ec81908991fc69855093707970d4a2c994c","tid":1440194,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"其實對家好明顯打緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意戰</span></span><br />\n所以我地係民意上絕對唔可以輸<br />\n當我地嘅文宣仲係留係痴街招等等<br />\n對家係今日已經係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">東方、明報、文匯</span></strong></span> 依三份報紙到登咗頭板全幅廣告 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公開撐警</span></span><br />\n所以我地要將個focus擺返係香港 <br />\n我地可以用兩日時間係628前係咁多個國家登頭版<br />\n亦都絕對可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一連一星期內洗香港各大報紙嘅頭版！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好多上咗年紀嘅人 仍然係鍾意用報紙來吸收資訊<br />\n塞撚爆各大報紙嘅頭版絕對係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打爆同溫層嘅好方法！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時依個方法亦都啱曬香港人嘅性格 與其捐錢買贖罪券 不如將啲錢真係投放係有用嘅地方做文宣！！！"},{"pid":"c80f136a28a4a166c153dd4ce577924137bffeb4","tid":1440194,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:09:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3019672738dc0324b2c896073180e946c9b75172","tid":1440194,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"自推十連！！！"},{"pid":"a4b46f3d616fd6e8bac2f11a29575149f8997a92","tid":1440194,"uid":68667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"大家幫推！！！"},{"pid":"1b892df6d33b4a40670d2b3436ff897b991a333b","tid":1440194,"uid":199838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d33842c11e314586ea63e9c0de592726c6f5911f","tid":1440194,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"眾籌"},{"pid":"8a13a14dc4fdf5637f4